{
  "message": "feat(conformance): add Series diff, shift, and pct_change conformance packets\n\nIntroduce five new strict-mode conformance packets for pandas Series\ntime-series operations that were previously untested:\n\n- fp_p2d_060_series_diff_periods_2_strict: validates Series.diff(periods=2)\n  producing correct NaN fill and element-wise subtraction\n- fp_p2d_060_series_diff_positive_periods_strict: validates Series.diff()\n  with default periods=1 behavior\n- fp_p2d_061_series_shift_negative_strict: validates Series.shift(-1) for\n  forward-looking alignment with trailing NaN\n- fp_p2d_061_series_shift_positive_strict: validates Series.shift(1) for\n  backward-looking alignment with leading NaN\n- fp_p2d_062_series_pct_change_strict: validates Series.pct_change()\n  fractional return computation with initial NaN\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
